Detailed Description

Checking the transmission counter at CUDA device.

Key actions:

  1. Open CUDA device
  2. Open gpumem driver
  3. Allocate three buffers in the CUDA memory
  4. Mapping buffers in the BAR1 space on CUDA device
  5. Filling the buffer 64-bit counter via BAR1
  6. Checking buffer in the CUDA device
  7. Decimation buffer and transfer to the HOST
  8. Transfer result of checking to HOST

Steps 5-8 are carried out in a loop
